ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectActs of the XXVI Congress of the Universal Postal union
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the ACTS OF THE XXVI CONGRESS OF THE UNIVERSAL POSTAL UNION that will be held in Istanbul from September 20 to October 7, 2016.
